{"title":"歌乐山，嘉陵江的漩涡","authors":["杨松杰"],"dates":[{"year":1995,"month":6,"day":26}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"歌乐山，嘉陵江的漩涡"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"杨松杰"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"歌乐山——一个浑浊的漩涡"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"嘉陵江水流到这里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"使一座美丽的山减了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"几分姿色"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山的美丽的名字后面"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——岁月的鞭痕"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"死亡摧残着正义"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"日日夜夜的星光下面"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"烈士的脸闪过方寸铁窗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"漩涡中有不灭的信仰"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"烈士有烈士之歌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"烈士有烈士之乐"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"烈士有烈士之山"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在我们淡忘了血腥之时"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和平的歌乐山"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"总有悲歌壮歌响彻"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"枕上的头颅"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"思悟着失眠"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"回忆小学课文上每一个汉字"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"启蒙永远地撞击着愚昧"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"撞击着灯红酒绿的麻木"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们必须不断地走入渣滓洞"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"闻那些刑具上血腥的锈蚀味"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"灵魂才能永生"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"嘉陵江的漩涡睁圆的瞳仁"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"以其为镜——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们真到了这个时候"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"照照我们"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":12,"page_end":12}